<h3 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h3><p><a href="https://arxiv.org/pdf/1408.5882.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Convolutional Neural Networks for Sentence Classification</a><br><a href="https://www.dynatrace.com/news/blog/why-averages-suck-and-percentiles-are-great/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">平均数与百分位数的性能</a><br><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/335347401" target="_blank" rel="noopener">停用词(Stop Words)的价值、收集与使用-李鹏宇</a><br><a href="https://wmathor.com/index.php/archives/1445/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TextCNN的PyTorch实现</a><br><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/366733135" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TextCNN+TorchText实现恶意程序分类</a><br><a href="https://lizitong67.github.io/2021/05/17/TextCNN-TorchText%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%81%B6%E6%84%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB/#4-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E8%AE%AD%E7%BB%83" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Torchtext实现恶意程序分类-收集参数-模型过程函数参数详解</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_43646592/article/details/113532455" target="_blank" rel="noopener">pytorch实现文本情感分类</a><br><a href="https://www.cxyzjd.com/article/kingsonyoung/90545746#33__284" target="_blank" rel="noopener">IMDB数据集分类-收集参数</a><br><a href="https://www.icode9.com/content-4-1024329.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">torchtext+TextCNN情感分类-代码解释详细</a><br><a href="https://www.jb51.net/article/212414.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">pytorch实现TextCNN+torchtext</a><br><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/yifanrensheng/p/13583443.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TensorFlow+TextCNN实现新闻分类-收集参数</a><br><a href="https://www.anquanke.com/post/id/193041" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TextCNN实现恶意软件检测-调参探究</a><br><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/77634533" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TextCNN原理+参数分析</a><br><a href="https://www.daimajiaoliu.com/daima/7125df61030f006" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TextCNN原理+自制图解</a><br><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/ModifyRong/p/11319301.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TextCNN原理</a><br><a href="https://lizec.top/2020/04/11/PyTorch%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0%E4%B9%8BTorchText/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">torchtext详解</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/bqw18744018044/article/details/109150802" target="_blank" rel="noopener">torchtext-Field详解</a><br><a href="https://www.daimajiaoliu.com/daima/4871a7573100403" target="_blank" rel="noopener">torchtext导入NLP数据集</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/jwoswin/article/details/92821752" target="_blank" rel="noopener">torchtext使用教程</a><br><a href="https://piqiandong.blog.csdn.net/article/details/110149143?spm=1001.2101.3001.6650.1&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2~default~BlogCommendFromBaidu~HighlightScore-1.queryctrv2&amp;depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant.none-task-blog-2~default~BlogCommendFromBaidu~HighlightScore-1.queryctrv2&amp;utm_relevant_index=2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">原理+实战-收集参数</a><br><a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/ModifyRong/p/11442661.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TextCNN优化经验-调参</a><br><a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26306795" target="_blank" rel="noopener">词向量Word2vec详解</a></p>
]]></content>
